
---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL ?? "/";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>AmicBridge – Lend, Borrow, Invest, Share Profit</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="AmicBridge is a modern platform where people can lend, borrow, invest and share profits in a transparent and structured way."
    />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f3f4f6;
        --white: #ffffff;
        --primary: #1d4ed8;
        --primary-soft: #e0e7ff;
        --border: #d1d5db;
        --text-main: #111827;
        --text-muted: #6b7280;
        --danger: #b91c1c;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text-main);
      }

      a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

      header {
        background: var(--white);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 16px 32px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
      .logo span { color: var(--primary); }

      nav { display: flex; gap: 24px; font-size: 14px; }
      nav a { color: var(--text-main); font-weight: 500; }

      .container { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 16px 56px; }

      .hero {
        margin-top: 24px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(0, 2fr);
        gap: 40px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .hero-main h1 { margin:0 0 12px; font-size:36px; }
      .hero-main p { margin:0 0 20px; font-size:16px; color:var(--text-muted); max-width:520px; }

      .hero-cta { display:flex; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; }

      .btn-primary {
        border:1px solid var(--primary);
        background:var(--primary);
        color:#fff;
        padding:10px 18px;
        border-radius:999px;
        font-size:14px;
        font-weight:600;
        cursor:pointer;
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--primary);
        border: 1px solid var(--primary-soft);
        padding: 10px 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 14px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .hero-card {
        background:var(--white);
        border:1px solid var(--border);
        padding:18px 20px;
        border-radius:8px;
        font-size:14px;
      }

      .hero-card-row {
        display:flex;
        justify-content:space-between;
        margin-bottom:8px;
      }

      .muted { color: var(--text-muted); }
      h2.section-title { font-size:22px; margin-top:40px; margin-bottom:12px; }

      .grid-3 {
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns:repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr));
        gap:20px;
      }

      .card {
        background:var(--white);
        border:1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius:8px;
        padding:16px 18px;
        font-size:14px;
      }

      .card h3 { margin:0 0 8px; font-size:16px; }
      .list { margin:0; padding-left:18px; color:var(--text-muted); }
      .list li { margin-bottom:4px; }

      .two-col {
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns:minmax(0,3fr) minmax(0,2fr);
        gap:24px;
      }

      .notice {
        background:#fef2f2;
        border:1px solid #fee2e2;
        color:var(--danger);
        padding:12px 14px;
        border-radius:6px;
        font-size:13px;
      }

      .contact-card {
        background:var(--white);
        border:1px solid var(--border);
        padding:16px 18px;
        border-radius:8px;
      }

      footer {
        border-top:1px solid var(--border);
        padding:16px 32px;
        font-size:12px;
        background:var(--white);
        color:var(--text-muted);
      }

      @media(max-width:900px){
        header{ padding:12px 16px; }
        .hero{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
        .two-col{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
        .grid-3{ grid-template-columns:1fr; }
        .hero-main h1{ font-size:28px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <div class="logo">AMIC<span>BRIDGE</span></div>

      <nav>
        <a href="#how-it-works">How it works</a>
        <a href="#products">Products</a>
        <a href="#agreements">Agreements</a>
        <a href="#safety">Safety</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-main">
          <h1>Lend. Borrow. Invest. Share the profit.</h1>

          <p>
            AmicBridge connects people who want to grow their money with people
            who need fair and transparent financing. Every deal through the
            AmicBridge network is supported by a written loan or investment
            agreement, so expectations are clear for everyone involved.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href="#contact">
              <button class="btn-primary">Contact CEO</button>
            </a>

            <a href="#products">
              <button class="btn-secondary">Explore Opportunities</button>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="hero-card">
          <div class="hero-card-row"><span class="muted">Platform</span><strong>P2P Lending & Investment</strong></div>
          <div class="hero-card-row"><span class="muted">Model</span><span>Profit Sharing</span></div>
          <div class="hero-card-row"><span class="muted">Focus</span><span>Written, Transparent Agreements</span></div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section id="how-it-works">
        <h2 class="section-title">How AmicBridge works</h2>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card"><h3>1. Lend & invest</h3><p>Provide capital with clear terms agreed in writing.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><h3>2. Borrow</h3><p>Funding for projects with structured repayment.</p></div>
          <div class="card"><h3>3. Share profit</h3><p>Fair profit sharing when projects succeed.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="products">
        <h2 class="section-title">Opportunities</h2>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Lending</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Fixed-term lending</li>
              <li>Clear returns</li>
              <li>Formal agreements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Borrowing</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Project-based funding</li>
              <li>Transparent repayment</li>
              <li>Legal clarity</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Profit sharing</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Aligned incentives</li>
              <li>Performance-based returns</li>
              <li>Written terms</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="agreements">
        <h2 class="section-title">Loan & Investment Agreements</h2>

        <div class="card">
          <p class="muted">
            When you make a deal through the AmicBridge network, you are not just “shaking hands online”.
            AmicBridge provides a structured written agreement for the deal.
          </p>

          <ul class="list">
            <li>Loan agreements for lending deals</li>
            <li>Investment or profit-sharing agreements for investment deals</li>
            <li>Clear description of responsibilities and expectations</li>
            <li>Protects both sides and avoids misunderstandings</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="safety">
        <h2 class="section-title">Safety & Transparency</h2>

        <div class="two-col">
          <div>
            <p class="muted">
              Lending and investing involve real financial risk. AmicBridge focuses on clarity,
              agreements, and structure so people understand what they are doing.
            </p>

            <ul class="list">
              <li>Every deal comes with a written agreement</li>
              <li>Clear expectations and timelines</li>
              <li>No hidden small print tricks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="notice">
            <strong>Important:</strong><br />
            AmicBridge is not a traditional bank. Returns are not guaranteed. Only commit money you can afford to risk.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact">
        <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>

        <div class="two-col">
          <div class="contact-card">
            <h3>Talk directly with the CEO</h3>
            <p>AmicBridge is led by <strong>Habbitx</strong>.</p>

            <p style="margin-top:10px;">
              Email:
              <a href="mailto:robertamicolsen@gmail.com">
                robertamicolsen@gmail.com
              </a>
            </p>

            <p class="muted" style="margin-top:10px;">
              Send whether you want to lend, borrow or invest and what type of deal you are interested in.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Include in your message</h3>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Your intent (lend / borrow / invest)</li>
              <li>Approximate amount</li>
              <li>Time frame</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
      © {new Date().getFullYear()} AmicBridge — Informational only, not financial advice
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
